for berries and grubs,

12:36.005 --> 12:38.799
and flicking at insects
with your sticky tongue,

12:38.967 --> 12:41.176
I feel a certain dismay.

12:41.344 --> 12:42.928
What are you talking about?

12:43.096 --> 12:45.389
