12:52.689 --> 12:53.772
What did we do wrong?

12:53.940 --> 12:56.191
Your error, surprisingly enough,

12:56.359 --> 12:58.277
is not to be a grotesque

12:58.445 --> 13:00.529
of inconceivable stupidity,

13:00.697 --> 13:02.531
but that you are white and male

13:02.699 --> 13:05.951
and not repulsively obese.

13:06.119 --> 13:07.953
