13:08.121 --> 13:09.538
I wonder if it lies

13:09.706 --> 13:11.915
in an excessive courtesy

13:12.083 --> 13:14.334
and eagerness to please.

13:15.753 --> 13:19.089
Shoo, skunk. Shoo.
Go go.

13:19.257 --> 13:21.133
Mr. Hearst.

13:21.301 --> 13:23.302
Farnum, have you
a moment for us to talk?

13:23.470 --> 13:26.346
